==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Disavowal
<hw>Dis`a*vow"al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
disavowing, disclaiming, or disowning; rejection and denial.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>An earnest <qex>disavowal</qex> of fear often proceeds from
fear.</q> <rj><qau>Richardson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Disavowance</ent>⟦br⟧
